  "announcement_github_body": "## Install leaf 0.9.1\n\n### Install prebuilt binaries via shell script\n\n```sh\ncurl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -LsSf https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-installer.sh | sh\n```\n\n### Install prebuilt binaries via powershell script\n\n```sh\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -c \"irm https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-installer.ps1 | iex\"\n```\n\n### Install prebuilt binaries via Homebrew\n\n```sh\nbrew install hoetaek/tap/leaf\n```\n\n## Download leaf 0.9.1\n\n|  File  | Platform | Checksum |\n|--------|----------|----------|\n| [leaf-aarch64-apple-darwin.tar.xz](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-aarch64-apple-darwin.tar.xz) | Apple Silicon macOS | [checksum](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-aarch64-apple-darwin.tar.xz.sha256) |\n| [leaf-x86_64-apple-darwin.tar.xz](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-x86_64-apple-darwin.tar.xz) | Intel macOS | [checksum](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-x86_64-apple-darwin.tar.xz.sha256) |\n| [leaf-aarch64-pc-windows-msvc.zip](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-aarch64-pc-windows-msvc.zip) | ARM64 Windows | [checksum](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-aarch64-pc-windows-msvc.zip.sha256) |\n| [leaf-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.zip](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.zip) | x64 Windows | [checksum](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.zip.sha256) |\n| [leaf-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.tar.xz](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.tar.xz) | x64 Linux | [checksum](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/releases/download/v0.9.1/leaf-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.tar.xz.sha256) |\n\n## Verifying GitHub Artifact Attestations\n\nThe artifacts in this release have attestations generated with GitHub Artifact Attestations. These can be verified by using the [GitHub CLI](https://cli.github.com/manual/gh_attestation_verify):\n```sh\ngh attestation verify <file-path of downloaded artifact> --repo hoetaek/leaf\n```\n\nYou can also download the attestation from [GitHub](https://github.com/hoetaek/leaf/attestations) and verify against that directly:\n```sh\ngh attestation verify <file-path of downloaded artifact> --bundle <file-path of downloaded attestation>\n```\n\n",
